HELM  ?  -package manager for k8s
  single user can serve docker container
  if million user ?cant serve so K8S -K8s cluster wil autoscale ,auto deploy,LB [lot of commd ]
  Managing k8s is big task  -so Helm chart (top of the  k8s) 
      helm chart provides top layer abstract with  minimal command  that internaly communicate with k8s

main commds:
[ helm repo add  -helm repo add bitnami https
  helm search  -helm search repo  bitnami |grep  -i argocd
  helm install  -helm install 
  helm list
  helm uninstall eks
]

if package not availbe ? add repo to helm 
  eg:aws eks
  1.search doc eg:helm repo add eks https..
  2.helm install alb1 eks/aws-load-balance    //under eks we have aws load balancer 

  popular repo :bitnamo
  command:helm repo add bitnami https:... [very usefule]
          under bitnami many repo available like prometoeius ,nginx...
          eg:helm install prometheous bitnami/prometheous   //prometheous  -user name

  create chart nd upload in repo -us eit 

  
